<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gray-adj">gray <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡreɪ/    美 /ɡreɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>灰 (色) 的；(毛发) 灰白的；灰暗的；苍白的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a grey sky
灰色的天空</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>grey hair
花白的头发</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was still looking gray and very tired.
他看上去仍然面色苍白，疲惫不堪。</p></div></div>